        protected void schedule(Job job)
        Description copied from class: Scheduler
        Schedule job to be executed. The scheduler implementation need only find a time to schedule the job based on whatever scheduling policy the schedule implements. This will be called again automatically if a job fails and it still has more attempts remaining.
